description: Cambridge Dictionary has added some 6,000 new words this year including 'delulu', a play on the word delusional, gibberish word 'skibidi' and 'tradwife', short for traditional wife.
title: Are you in a 'parasocial' relationship? Cambridge Dictionary makes it the word of the year after rise in trend

description: Police and the press will be free to reveal more about suspects under proposed new contempt of court laws to prevent a repeat of the Southport riots.
title: Freedom of speech victory as contempt laws set for overhaul after Southport riots
